{"tid":141083,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有無同過有暴力傾向嘅人一齊？","createTime":"2017-03-02T15:40:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T06:04:59.000Z","uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c2b00d70dec74c0d14c4619cf13d45c5804adce","tid":141083,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:40:31.000Z","msg":"好大陰影<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ca2c193e07c4c43aa67f1d5c7ac20c31c7629e","tid":141083,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:41:41.000Z","msg":"佢對你做過乜？"},{"pid":"8b198cfb00d60d1a76bf86c88d6ba3d8862d79d4","tid":141083,"uid":15960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:19:05.000Z","msg":"一齊打場架先"},{"pid":"207fef6f31dd7516d949150a297c9bdd8dff3ff3","tid":141083,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:54:55.000Z","msg":"你好唔好打？"},{"pid":"b3c97efb3698fb39f98de81ee7df721fad4aa563","tid":141083,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:55:37.000Z","msg":"會點"},{"pid":"09c1c6ba38e22335ed6569807a620dd3fb071601","tid":141083,"uid":49228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:55:40.000Z","msg":"佢點打你？"},{"pid":"7ae739bb2ec3daa80182b4cf6272928b7c4d911e","tid":141083,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:59:46.000Z","msg":"啲有暴力傾向嘅人<br />\n好易好少事就嬲 發晒脾氣<br />\n當初我傻 仲以為你只係脾氣有少少唔好<br />\n但原來唔係"},{"pid":"cb5c8f4007aada532ac1397ffab927d7f7f38c23","tid":141083,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:00:20.000Z","msg":"最憎d脾氣既人"},{"pid":"b567d1f6c469f25c499a0acfc109c66413d679a1","tid":141083,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:00:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最憎d脾氣既人</blockquote><br />\n脾氣差"},{"pid":"eb5d62c79ccc24d4146141e00c12367c6baa2903","tid":141083,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:03:42.000Z","msg":"你本身脾氣已經唔好<br />\n而對我 你更加係零容忍<br />\n好少事就可以大大聲鬧我 講晒粗口<br />\n同你一齊果啲時間 係我由出世到宜家聽過最多最難聽 最不堪入耳嘅說話<br />\n有一啲真係一想講返出口 已經出唔到聲忍唔住想喊<br />\n<br />\n或者我有時響連登嘅毒舌都係學咗你<br />\n但當然你勁我十倍"},{"pid":"c2ec937f4021444e08582b94f9c9daf43ba062b0","tid":141083,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:03:46.000Z","msg":"分左未<br />\n一個願打，，，"},{"pid":"6786bbe07ecf57ed708cf045b052c8e35219a83d","tid":141083,"uid":80507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:05:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你本身脾氣已經唔好<br />\n而對我 你更加係零容忍<br />\n好少事就可以大大聲鬧我 講晒粗口<br />\n同你一齊果啲時間 係我由出世到宜家聽過最多最難聽 最不堪入耳嘅說話<br />\n有一啲真係一想講返出口 已經出唔到聲忍唔住想喊<br />\n<br />\n或者我有時響連登嘅毒舌都係學咗你<br />\n但當然你勁我十倍</blockquote><br />\n對最親既人都脾氣差真係唔要得<br />\n想像唔到點樣對住佢忍成世 早走早著啦絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d74a7ed074782804d809255ebbd6f9da5a9228","tid":141083,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:06:30.000Z","msg":"本身我脾氣都唔算好<br />\n但因為曾經好愛你<br />\n所以我會默默忍受<br />\n就算唔係我錯 我都會氹你<br />\n<br />\n但你無珍惜過 反而變本加厲<br />\n你個人根本性格係好有問題"},{"pid":"f8ed01b5064843b097727e4ed38f127f2881242b","tid":141083,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:11:45.000Z","msg":"佢唔係毒打我果種 唔係一次性好嚴重拳打腳踢<br />\n而係試過好大力拍我塊面 打我個頭<br />\n好大力推我 試過有一次 佢發晒脾氣要走<br />\n我追住佢 佢好大力練住我頸練起咗我<br />\n我成個人離咗地（我好細粒好輕）"},{"pid":"889074043b46c57a055ea0b243140ed9aa7f7d85","tid":141083,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:12:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分左未<br />\n一個願打，，，</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n分<br />\n但佢仲有嘢爭我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔會再做軟弱嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ec9198f757a74a350d86e370b3afed23f932c8","tid":141083,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:14:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你好唔好打？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我好想唔會開post<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都想打贏為自己出啖氣"},{"pid":"5588e96b95d8eddc224b86dd0186ede1c46cb2f6","tid":141083,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:24:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>分左未<br />\n一個願打，，，</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n分<br />\n但佢仲有嘢爭我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔會再做軟弱嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n勞資糾紛？"},{"pid":"6ce3c495bb8d1fa6b049d52c9f0cf648d720e20d","tid":141083,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:26:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你好唔好打？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我好想唔會開post<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都想打贏為自己出啖氣</blockquote><br />\n血 不可白流<br />\n流多少 便吃多少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d329dd3305cb49f578bf141d49ac4b03c04904","tid":141083,"uid":36092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:27:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>分左未<br />\n一個願打，，，</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n分<br />\n但佢仲有嘢爭我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔會再做軟弱嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n勞資糾紛？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f805c7ef28c139ec7d10dbfc521bef1b86b3ae1e","tid":141083,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep