quote><br />\n<br />\n之後有講返 佢話好心痛 我心諗 收皮啦心痛你又打<br />\n差d報警 有次佢練完我條頸我鬆開左 拎起電話打俾我朋友話救命快d幫我報警 不過佢又對住我係到喊 我又心軟"},{"pid":"331dc16e2dc639b81a9eebc3234891f7a7f2ae5c","tid":141083,"uid":65142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T21:56:06.000Z","msg":"當局者迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前睇lastfriends(講暴力男既日劇)都唔明女主角點解唔分手，但一發生係自己身上就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次佢一喊住同我講冇下次我就心軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知佢都唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申： 已分，但每次一諗起佢依然會好掛住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e5241c00aadbbbdcda4d5ca86bf57f64985161","tid":141083,"uid":74442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T22:14:07.000Z","msg":"郁手郁腳都唔飛，等樓主上報"},{"pid":"206b378a9dc612394244c1c368a9712941ee935c","tid":141083,"uid":16275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T22:38:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你本身脾氣已經唔好<br />\n而對我 你更加係零容忍<br />\n好少事就可以大大聲鬧我 講晒粗口<br />\n同你一齊果啲時間 係我由出世到宜家聽過最多最難聽 最不堪入耳嘅說話<br />\n有一啲真係一想講返出口 已經出唔到聲忍唔住想喊<br />\n<br />\n或者我有時響連登嘅毒舌都係學咗你<br />\n但當然你勁我十倍</blockquote><br />\n好似我對上個ex咁<br />\n每忍多佢一日返到屋企就更憎自己多一啲<br />\n最黎灑脫分手！"},{"pid":"ccd312a7e08d49068c589c6502879878892e59e3","tid":141083,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T22:46:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>郁手郁腳都唔飛，等樓主上報</blockquote><br />\n好女仔"},{"pid":"0b41955185a0a7c3fe2394f8a7340254fe61d671","tid":141083,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:34:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁似我中學女神既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢又係比男友打 <br />\n聽講有次想唔知做乜 我女神唔制比佢係地鐵站捉去角落打佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拳拳到肉定點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽講佢男友初頭扮好仔係佢屋企人面前<br />\n但已經成日無啦啦發脾氣<br />\n一齊左陣已經會掉野掉佢<br />\n後來變到會用手mit瘀佢 最後會用拳頭打肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽番黎都覺得痴線咁都忍得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來分手又係死纏住 日日打上佢屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拖咗幾耐先分到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依啲人真係要睇醫生 但佢唔會覺得自己有問題 而就算覺得有都唔會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要面可能<br />\n你朋友宜家會唔會好大陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多人最大既問題<br />\n就係唔會望下自己有無問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都有自己問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唔會咁樣傷害人<br />\n用暴力凌駕一切真係好恐怖"},{"pid":"88500240afc459c21c3b1f8d6cc04d0c23b710e4","tid":141083,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:36:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明白樓主 真係好撚大陰影 <br />\n個個都話點解可以逼到個咁善良既人出手 因為佢個時做左d極無恥既野 然後打我 我忍唔住都打左佢<br />\n頂左呢條友兩年 分左手都仲係好大陰影 諗起就會覺得好驚 覺得自己都痴痴地線<br />\n<br />\n初期佢成日係街少少事就發顛 又踢野又掟野 <br />\n最嚴重有一次仲去我學校踢爆左門口塊玻璃搞到要賠錢 <br />\n仲有次試過係apm大堂個到踢跌左個垃圾桶 個到勁多人 我自己執返起個垃圾桶 真係好撚委屈 勁驚俾人拍片 勁多人係到指指點點<br />\n<br />\n後期就成日係屋企打交 嘈到成屋人都知 唉 每次諗返起同佢打交既畫面都覺得好恐怖 呢個人係惡魔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你最後點同佢分手咖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得如果夠打根本唔驚佢<br />\n但唔夠打真係痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好恐怖"},{"pid":"6845f0cbadbabf080a3fed110daf66ffc96bcc01","tid":141083,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:38:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁似我中學女神既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢又係比男友打 <br />\n聽講有次想唔知做乜 我女神唔制比佢係地鐵站捉去角落打佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拳拳到肉定點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽講佢男友初頭扮好仔係佢屋企人面前<br />\n但已經成日無啦啦發脾氣<br />\n一齊左陣已經會掉野掉佢<br />\n後來變到會用手mit瘀佢 最後會用拳頭打肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽番黎都覺得痴線咁都忍得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來分手又係死纏住 日日打上佢屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拖咗幾耐先分到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依啲人真係要睇醫生 但佢唔會覺得自己有問題 而就算覺得有都唔會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要面可能<br />\n你朋友宜家會唔會好大陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拖左成個月又一齊番 痴撚線<br />\n過幾日就分左 條仔又黎料<br />\n<br />\n過左差唔多一年佢拍番拖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宜家男朋友對佢好好？"},{"pid":"a2409ba5791c5076fa3d84add41070b0696fdd11","tid":141083,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:39:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢唔係毒打我果種 唔係一次性好嚴重拳打腳踢<br />\n而係試過好大力拍我塊面 打我個頭<br />\n好大力推我 試過有一次 佢發晒脾氣要走<br />\n我追住佢 佢好大力練住我頸練起咗我<br />\n我成個人離咗地（我好細粒